text: Lisa Gründing (born 2 December 1991) is a German volleyball player. == Career == She played for TSV Burgdorf, and SC Potsdam. She participated in the 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. and 2019 Montreux Volley Masters. == References == == External links == * FIVB profile * CEV profile * * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:German women's volleyball players Category:People from Burgwedel
